title: San Fernando
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Middle Eastern, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Turkish and Moroccan cuisine with choices for vegans like salads, hummus and flatbread, wraps, falafel, rice, chochouka. Cost is approx. 17 euros for food and one drink per person. The owner will advise about what is vegetarian.
